4\'2e Employee recruitment and selection (allowance 2/2)\line
5\'2e Employee hiring and orientation (allowance 2/2)\line
6\'2e Performance management and appraisal (allowance 4/4)\line
7\'2e Employee compensation and benefits (allowance 2/2)\line
8\'2e Employee training and development (allowance 2/2)\line
9\'2e Working conditions and labour relations (allowance 4/4)\line
10\'2e Human resource information system (allowance 2/2)}\cell\row\pard
